task.summary: Default task
New way to create/edit servers. Now a addon can use the properties from the parent. And many methods now uses an addon instead of a string.
Little clean-up.
Alpha 0.4.13.9 Addons: 0.0.1.1
Alpha 0.4.13.9 Addons: 0.0.1.1
Design are now spilt in many files. This is to make the designs more readable.
Some GUI-improvements and cli-parser.
Added command history
Added new settings api, multithreading-optimizations and scenicView for debugging
Added handling for invalid jar paths.
Added test support
Now the addon loader decides by the version, if duplicate addons are present.
Use another way to load designs (fixed bug #1)
Re-added addon-loader dialog
Added gradle task to clear jarCopys folder
Update libraries.
The server console now display an error in output, if the server can't start. (Fixed #10)
Now the servercontroller saves all logs into .servercontroller/logs/... (Fixed #8)
Code and performance improvements
Code and performance improvements
Added context menu to TreeEntry
Fixed bug with whitespace (fixed #2)
Re-added scrollbar in console output (fixed #11)
Better way to implement the last commit.
Now the addons are copied into a temp folder to prevent write on a used file.
Added (hopefully) support for jenkins build number
Added build number to jar manifest
Alpha 0.4.14
Completely new api to work the tabview and treeview. This new system supports tab-in-tabs and can be very useful for other things
Vanilla Plugin 0.0.1.2 Works with new api
Craftbukkit Addon 0.0.1.2 Works with new api
Spigot Addon 0.0.1.2 Works with new api
BungeeCord Addon 0.0.1.2
Added text editor for editing server files
Fixed and improved some things with the new api
Added accent colors
Re-added server edit function and fixed other things
Added support for multiple file editors.
Added basic image viewer
Added error dialog if there are error while an addon is loading. (fixed #13)
Added bright-rework design
Improved support for new api in vanilla addon
Fixed error that the servercontroller doesn't start if the design id is wrong (fixed #15)
Renamed module from servercontroller to servercontroller-core
Added missing files
Renamed servercontroller module to servercontroller-core.
Merged servercontroller-api into a sub-project. This is currently no finished.
Added AddonRegistry to make the way to register things easier.
Fixed addons and core.
